Sprunki Sonic: A Creative Sonic-Themed Music Experience
Sprunki Sonic is an exciting online mod of the classic Sprunki game that features all your favorite Sonic characters! With intuitive drag-and-drop controls, you can create custom music tracks effortlessly. Characters like Tails, Amy, Knuckles, and Metal Sonic each bring their own unique sounds and vibes, letting you mix and match to craft amazing musical combos.

This mod is so simple and fun that anyone can jump in and start creating! Whether you're a hardcore Sonic fan or just love music games, Sprunki Sonic promises endless creativity and entertainment.
